data.name: max_open_local_content
data.primary_definition: max value possible for local content if all awardings are fully local. Takes into account import goods and expat labor from skills percentages/salaires

data.name: total_local_content
data.primary_definition: prime_local_content + locally_awarded_local_content

data.name: prime_local_content
data.primary_definition: labor_salary_local + goods_domestic + some portion of oga for goods and labor (based on portion of goods/labor done locally)

data.name: locally_awarded_local_content
data.primary_definition: labor_salary_local + labor_oga + labor_profit  + goods_domestic + goods_profit + goods_oga (for both fully local and subcontract awardings)

data.name: fullocal_local_content
data.primary_definition: local content associated with fully local contracts

data.name: subk_local_content
data.primary_definition: local content associated with subcontracts

data.name: total_value
data.primary_definition: Total Value of the project

data.name: total_labor
data.primary_definition: Total labor in project (includes profit and OGA)

data.name: total_goods
data.primary_definition: Total goods in project (includes profit and OGA)

data.name: open_value
data.primary_definition: Amount of project that is open for local bidding

data.name: open_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor that is open for local bidding

data.name: open_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods that is open for local bidding

data.name: non_open_value
data.primary_definition: Amount of project that was not open for local bidding

data.name: non_open_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor that was not open for local bidding

data.name: non_open_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods that was not open for local bidding

data.name: fully_local_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor that was awarded to a local full via a full contract

data.name: fully_local_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods that was awarded to a local full via a full contract

data.name: prime_awarded_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor that was awarded to a Pime contractor

data.name: prime_awarded_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods that was awarded to a Pime contractor

data.name: prime_subcontracted_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor awarded to a Prime contractor, but subcontracted to a local firm

data.name: prime_labor_salary_local
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor awarded to a Prime contractor that was used to hire local workers

data.name: prime_labor_salary_expat
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor awarded to a Prime contractor that was used to hire expat workers

data.name: prime_labor_profit
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor awarded to a Prime contractor that went to profit

data.name: prime_labor_oga_local
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor awarded to a Prime contractor that went to oga

data.name: prime_labor_oga_foreign
data.primary_definition: Amount of prime labor oga that counts to local content

data.name: prime_subcontracted_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods awarded to a Prime contractor, but subcontracted to a local firm

data.name: prime_goods_domestic
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods awarded to a Prime contractor that were domestic

data.name: prime_goods_import
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods awarded to a Prime contractor that were imported

data.name: prime_goods_profit
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods awarded to a Prime contractor that went to profit

data.name: prime_goods_oga_local
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods awarded to a Prime contractor that went to oga

data.name: prime_goods_oga_foreign
data.primary_definition: Amount of prime goods oga that counts to local content

data.name: locally_awarded_labor
data.primary_definition: Amount of labor that was awarded to a local firm either by full contract or subcontract

data.name: locally_awarded_goods
data.primary_definition: Amount of goods that was awarded to a local firm either by full contract or subcontract

data.name: locally_awarded_total_value
data.primary_definition: All value associated with local awardings: either fully local or subcontracted = fullocal_total_value + subk_total_value

data.name: fullocal_total_value
data.primary_definition: All value associated with fully local contracts. Should be fully_local_labor + fully_local_goods

data.name: subk_total_value
data.primary_definition: All value associated with subcontrated work. Should be prime_subcontracted_labor + prime_subcontracted_goods

data.name: max_open_total_value
data.primary_definition: max value possible for locally awarding = open_value
